is worth taking to hell with me.

49
00:11:24,977 --> 00:11:27,938
Goodbye, Mr. Kim.

50
00:11:40,117 --> 00:11:42,244
Oh... Hi, Jeong Jian.

51
00:11:44,955 --> 00:11:47,124
