- Okay.
- So sensitive.

108
00:17:29,633 --> 00:17:31,510
- So sensitive.
- I'm not sensitive!

109
00:17:31,593 --> 00:17:33,470
- You're disgusting.
- She's always like this.

110
00:17:33,554 --> 00:17:34,555
