147
00:19:52,609 --> 00:19:53,610
Second,

148
00:19:53,694 --> 00:19:55,320
your tutor, Kim Jinki...

149
00:19:56,780 --> 00:19:58,907
Well, in the end,

150
00:19:58,991 --> 00:20:01,535
