175
00:21:30,666 --> 00:21:31,667
Well?

176
00:21:35,963 --> 00:21:37,965
Then, make a bet with me.

177
00:21:40,425 --> 00:21:41,426
My face.

178
00:21:42,135 --> 00:21:45,097
