that everyone talks about?

186
00:22:16,753 --> 00:22:18,630
Honestly, I don't remember.

187
00:22:21,216 --> 00:22:22,676
Isn't it time you told me?

188
00:22:30,475 --> 00:22:31,810
Will you take the bet?

189
00:22:33,645 --> 00:22:36,356
It took a lot for me
to bring this up to you!

190
00:22:37,482 --> 00:22:38,650
What's wrong with you?

191
00:22:39,276 --> 00:22:40,861
