226
00:25:08,550 --> 00:25:09,718
Let go!

227
00:25:09,801 --> 00:25:11,220
Let go of me!

228
00:25:11,720 --> 00:25:13,096
Hey! Let go!

229
00:25:18,352 --> 00:25:19,353
Let...

230
00:25:38,705 --> 00:25:40,145
